identity-link-private-only = For security, link platform accounts in a private chat with the bot.
identity-link-code =
    Your one-time platform link code: {$code}
    On the other platform, send: osu account {$code}
    Available platforms:
    {$bot_links}
    The code expires in {$minutes} minutes. The account that generated the code remains the primary account.
identity-link-success = Accounts linked. Connected platforms: {$platforms}.
identity-link-already-linked = These accounts are already linked. Connected platforms: {$platforms}.
identity-link-invalid-token = The link code is invalid or has expired. Generate a new code on the primary platform.
identity-link-same-account = Open the bot on another platform and enter this code there.
identity-link-platform-conflict = The accounts cannot be merged because both identities already contain: {$platforms}.
